- Use parameterized queries to prevent SQL injection attacks
- Implement proper indexing to optimize query performance
- Use transactions for maintaining data integrity in multi-step operations
- Regularly update statistics and run VACUUM to maintain database performance
- Use EXPLAIN ANALYZE to optimize complex queries
- Implement connection pooling to manage database connections efficiently
- Use appropriate data types to ensure data integrity and optimize storage
